title: Escape the Night... What really happened ft Joey Graceffa
description:
What’s up Fool Fam! This week Manny and Laura invite the one and only Joey Graceffa! They talk about how they met, launching his new zodiac collection, what’s next for his channel, his view on the Escape the Night + Gabbie Hanna drama, and much more! Also Manny shares a very cringy hookup encounter…
